translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 翌日――

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kesselring did not appear during the night,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっ、あーーー……

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ugh, Lord Rance was so intense yesterday, my hips..."

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At that moment, Sheila entered with a radiant smile like a large flower.
